<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 1542/1999 </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 1542/1999, </eesti>
<inglise> of 14 July 1999 fixing the actual production of olive oil and the unit amount of production aid for the 1997/98 marketing year </inglise>
<eesti> millega m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks oliivi&otilde;li tegelik toodang ja tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;r &uuml;hiku kohta 1997/98. turustusaastaks </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> 14. juuli 1999 EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation No 136/66/EEC of 22 September 1966 on the establishment of a common organisation of the market in oils and fats(1), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1638/98(2), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 22. septembri 1966. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust nr 136/66/EM&Uuml; &otilde;li- ja rasvaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kehtestamise kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1638/98, (2) </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Regulation (EC) No 1638/98, and in particular Article 3(1) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 1638/98, eriti selle artikli 3 l&otilde;iget 1, </eesti>
<inglise> (1) Whereas Regulation (EC) No 1638/98 introduces major changes in the common organisation of the market in oils and fats from 1 November 1998; whereas the olive oil production aid scheme in particular has been overhauled; whereas, to ensure smooth transition between the schemes in force before and after 1 November 1998, it is necessary to lay down provisions for the production aid for the 1997/98 marketing year, to apply up to the end of that year; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: 1) m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) 1638/98 tehakse &otilde;li- ja rasvaturu &uuml;hises korralduses alates 1. novembrist 1998 suuremaid muudatusi; eelk&otilde;ige on uuendatud oliivi&otilde;li tootmistoetuse kava; sujuva &uuml;lemineku tagamiseks enne 1. novembrit 1998 kehtinud kavalt p&auml;rast seda kuup&auml;eva kehtivale kavale on vaja ette n&auml;ha 1997/98. turustusaasta tootmistoetust k&auml;sitlevate s&auml;tete kohaldamine k&otilde;nealuse aasta l&otilde;pus; </eesti>
<inglise> (2) Whereas Article 5 of Regulation No 136/66/EEC in the version applicable on 31 October 1998 provides that the unit amount of the production aid must be reduced where the actual production for a given marketing year exceeds the maximum guaranteed quantity fixed for that marketing year; whereas, however, producers whose average production is less than 500 kilograms of olive oil per marketing year are not affected by that reduction; </inglise>
<eesti> 2) m&auml;&auml;ruse nr 136/66/EM&Uuml; 31. oktoobril 1998 kehtiva redaktsiooni artiklis 5 s&auml;testatakse, et tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;ra &uuml;hiku kohta peab v&auml;hendama, kui asjaomase turustusaasta tegelik toodang &uuml;letab selle turustusaasta jaoks kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud garanteeritud maksimumkogust; siiski ei m&otilde;juta see v&auml;hendamine tootjaid, kelle keskmine toodang on v&auml;iksem kui 500 kilogrammi oliivi&otilde;li turustusaasta kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> (3) Whereas Article 17a of Council Regulation (EEC) No 2261/84(3), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1639/98(4), in the version applicable on 31 October 1998, provides that, in order to determine the unit amount of the production aid for olive oil which may be paid in advance, the estimated production for the marketing year concerned should be established; whereas, for the 1997/98 marketing year, the estimated production and the unit amount of production aid which may be paid in advance were fixed by Commission Regulation (EC) No 2095/98(5); </inglise>
<eesti> 3) m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2261/84 (3) (viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1639/98 (4)) 31. oktoobril 1998 kehtiva redaktsiooni artiklis 17a s&auml;testatakse, et oliivi&otilde;li ettemakstava tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;ra kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramiseks &uuml;hiku kohta tuleks kehtestada asjaomase turustusaasta hinnanguline toodang; 1997/98. turustusaasta hinnanguline toodang ja ettemakstav tootmistoetus &uuml;hiku kohta on kindlaks m&auml;&auml;ratud komisjoni m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 2095/98; (5) </eesti>
<inglise> (4) Whereas, pursuant to Article 17a(3) of Regulation (EEC) No 2261/84 in the version applicable on 31 October 1998, not more than eight months after the end of the marketing year, the quantity actually produced in respect of which entitlement to the aid has been recognised must be determined; whereas, to that end, in accordance with Article 12a of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 3061/84(6), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 2455/97(7), the Member States concerned must notify the Commission, not later than 31 May following each marketing year, of the quantity recognised as qualifying for the aid in each Member State; whereas, as a result of those communications, the quantity eligible for aid for the 1997/98 marketing year amounts to 712847 tonnes for Italy, 2480 tonnes for France, 492364 tonnes for Greece, 1147000 tonnes for Spain and 39600 tonnes for Portugal; </inglise>
<eesti> 4) vastavalt m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2261/84 31. oktoobri 1998 kehtiva redaktsiooni artikli 17a l&otilde;ikele 3 tuleb hiljemalt kaheksa kuu jooksul p&auml;rast turustusaasta l&otilde;ppu kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata tegelikult toodetud kogused, mille puhul on tunnustatud abi saamise &otilde;igust; selleks peavad asjaomased liikmesriigid vastavalt komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3061/84 (6) (viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 2455/97 (7)) artiklile 12a teatama komisjonile hiljemalt iga j&auml;rgmise turustusaasta 31. maiks k&otilde;nealuses liikmesriigis abi saamise tingimustele vastava koguse; k&otilde;nealuse teavitamise j&auml;rgi on toetuse saamise tingimustele vastavad kogused 1997/98. turustusaastal Itaalia puhul 712 847 tonni, Prantsusmaa puhul 2480 tonni, Kreeka puhul 492 364 tonni, Hispaania puhul 1 147 000 tonni ja Portugali puhul 39 600 tonni; </eesti>
<inglise> (5) Whereas recognition by the Member States of those quantities as qualifying for the aid implies that the checks referred to in Regulations (EEC) No 2261/84 and (EEC) No 3061/84 have been carried out; whereas, however, fixing actual production in accordance with the information on the quantities recognised as qualifying for Community aid by the Member States does not prejudge the conclusions that may be drawn from verification of the accuracy of that information under the clearance of accounts procedure; </inglise>
<eesti> 5) k&otilde;nealuste koguste tunnustamine liikmesriikide poolt abi saamise tingimustele vastavatena eeldab, et on l&auml;bi viidud m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 2261/84 ja m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 3061/84 osutatud kontrollid; tegeliku toodangu kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramine vastavalt teabele koguste kohta, mida liikmesriigid on tunnustanud &uuml;henduse abi saamise tingimustele vastavatena, ei piira raamatupidamisarvestuse kontrollimise ja heakskiitmise k&auml;igus k&otilde;nealuse teabe &otilde;igsuse kontrollimise tulemusena tehtavaid v&otilde;imalikke j&auml;reldusi; </eesti>
<inglise> (6) Whereas, in view of the quantity actually produced, the unit amount of the production aid provided for in point (b) of the fifth subparagraph of Article 5(1) of Regulation No 136/66/EEC in the version applicable on 31 October 1998 should also be fixed; </inglise>
<eesti> 6) pidades silmas tegelikult toodetud koguseid, tuleks samuti kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata m&auml;&auml;ruse nr 136/66/EM&Uuml; 31. oktoobril 1998 kehtiva redaktsiooni artikli 5 l&otilde;ike 1 viienda l&otilde;igu punktis b etten&auml;htud tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;r &uuml;hiku kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> (7) Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Oils and Fats, </inglise>
<eesti> 7) k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las &otilde;li- ja rasvaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> For the 1997/98 olive oil marketing year: </inglise>
<eesti> 1997/98. turustusaastal on oliivi&otilde;li: </eesti>
<inglise> - the quantity actually produced in respect of which entitlement to the production aid has been recognised is 2394291 tonnes, </inglise>
<eesti> - tegelikult toodetud kogus, mille puhul on tunnustatud &otilde;igust tootmistoetust saada, 2 394 291 tonni, </eesti>
<inglise> - the unit amount of the production aid shall be EUR 80,17 per 100 kilograms. </inglise>
<eesti> - tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;r &uuml;hiku kohta 80,17 eurot 100 kilogrammi kohta. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the seventh day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub seitsmendal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 14 July 1999. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 14. juuli 1999 </eesti>
